reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best fan for your personal space!
reviews.reviewText: There is nothing not to like about this fan. It hangs on a hook it stands up. It has several speeds to choose from, and it delivers a nice fresh flow of air.I simply love it I use it in my RV Please read before buying:I purchased this item to cover my leather bench cushion in my motorhome. My vision is 25” wide x 75” length x 6” height.The sellers description is: 27.5"D x 75"W x 9"HIt fit great length wise and the width, barely making it over the edge, which creates the height as you can see from the photo. 1 inch is uncovered, and the height of my cushion is 6 inches.The Sellers’s description says it’s it’s up to 9 inches. NOT possible! Needless to say, it covered the majority of my cushion, which only serves as a platform for a mattress topper that I put on it at night to sleep on, so that being said, I don’t care much and I’m just going to use it, however it is less 1 inch towards the bottom, which you really can’t see unless you get close. The price was very cheap and I should be concerned about that with future purchases, and look to invest in better quality. The material is cheap. It almost feels like half material and half rubber. There are many nice fabrics out there that they can use that are still stretchy. When you hold it up to the light you should not be able to see through it.To end my review, I just want to say to be aware that it will stretch to 75” in length but no longer than that . Width wise it will stretch to 25” and borrow a little bit from the height, but it will NOT cover more than about 3 or 4 inches in height. Definitely not 9 inches.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Powerful and Quiet
reviews.reviewText: I bought this fan for a trip, but it's already become a new friend at home. It's smaller, flatter, lighter, quieter and more powerful than I thought it would be. Powerful fan, long-lasting battery, extra quiet. I've also carried it with me outside in the sun. Great deal.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: So far so good with this product. Super quiet. Perfect in my office setting. Tilts as well. Hopefully hardware will last longer than a year fingers crossed. Very nice !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little fan
reviews.reviewText: I needed a small fan for my bathroom vanity while I was getting ready for my day. This one fits what i was looking for - small, rechargeable, quiet, and it shows how much battery you have left. The only knock I have on it is that the battery does go down somewhat quickly but it does last several days without charging. There are different speeds and it’s easy to charge. I highly recommend!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works really good
reviews.reviewText: Perfect size & not noisy at all. I like how the battery life displays & the different speeds.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small but powerful!
reviews.reviewText: I love this little fan. It's small but blows out good air. The only thing is the charge doesn't hold long. So be prepared to constantly charge it. Good thing it let's you know what level it's on. I have 2 and exchange them out. When one needs charging I use the other one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Strong airflow and quiet on lowest setting
reviews.reviewText: Battery lasts a few hours but, on the lowest setting it is whisper quiet and pushes a really nice amount of air flow from 12 to 24 inches away. Item is very light but, sturdy plastic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is a very effective little fan
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this fan because of its discrete profile. I plug it into a backup battery and it lasts for more than eight hours. I have never seen the battery drop below 90%. It’s pretty impressive and it accomplishes the job. And only $10 this was an incredible value.
Love this fan, it's a perfect size for carrying in my purse...I use it everywhere!

reviews.reviewTitle: Where has this been all my life?!
reviews.reviewText: This is GREAT. Get it! Keep it in your purse! Your pocket! Your Fanny pack!

I do love this fan for being compact and the 2 settings are strong enough to get a great fan. I gave it a 4 rating bc one negative is the power button can be easily pressed by something rubbing or touching it so it will go on and then the batter is wasted bc you didn’t know it was turned on my accident.
